Update Shape Text as per Visio® Interop API for Python Apps
item.description: Aspose.Diagram for Python via .NET 22.8 Download  Support Forum  File Details Downloads: 1 File Size: 110.6MB Date Added: 9/8/2022 Release Noteshttps://releases.aspose.com/diagram/python-net/release-notes/2022/aspose-diagram-for-python-via-net-22-8-release-notes/ DescriptionAspose.Diagram for Python via .NET 22.8 File Details Add Points to Dynamic Connector Shape This API release offers the ability to add points to the dynamic connector shape. Update Shape as per Visio®/Interop It was observed that the shape was not being updating as per Visio®/Interop after text is added.

item.title: Validation Rule Set in Visio® Diagrams API for Python Apps
item.description: Aspose.Diagram for Python via .NET 22.9 Download  Support Forum  File Details Downloads: 1 File Size: 110.61MB Date Added: 14/9/2022 Release Noteshttps://releases.aspose.com/diagram/python-net/release-notes/2022/aspose-diagram-for-python-via-net-22-9-release-notes/ DescriptionAspose.Diagram for Python via .NET 22.9 File Details View Visio® Diagram Validation Rule Sets It was observed that the RuleSets were not being appeared in the Visio® diagram validation data. This issue has now been resolved. Improved VSDX to SVG Conversion While converting the Visio® VSDX to SVG, in some instances it was observed that all the text in the boxes was being gotten over the box border lines.

item.title: Visio® to SVG, Visio® to HTML Conversion API for Python Apps
item.description: Aspose.Diagram for Python via .NET 22.10 Download  Support Forum  File Details Downloads: 1 File Size: 110.62MB Date Added: 17/10/2022 Release Noteshttps://releases.aspose.com/diagram/python-net/release-notes/2022/aspose-diagram-for-python-via-net-22-10-release-notes/ DescriptionAspose.Diagram for Python via .NET 22.10 File Details Improved Visio® to SVG Export It was observed that a Visio® graphic is being displayed in poor quality when it is exported to SVG format. This issue has now been resolved.

item.title: Convert Visio® Diagram VSDX to PDF via API for Python Apps
